Sentence-level editing, or SLE for short, is a proposal for a new, usable editor for Mediawiki. It's aimed at providing an editor that offers just basic functionality: editing sentences.

For more information, check this page: http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/User:JanPaul123/Sentence-level_editing

